    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so excited to show you this beauty. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it that it practically looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy\u2014spotless inside and out, with a finish that really pops in the sun. It drives like a total dream, super smooth and responsive. If you've been looking for that perfect 'new car' feel without the crazy dealership markup, you\u2019ve found it! I'm happy to chat and show you around the car whenever you're free. Hope to hear from you soon!",
      "price": 44500.0,
