    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 power plant. This unit is mechanically impeccable, showcasing a high-pressure double-VANOS system with zero rattle and a crisp 8,000 RPM redline facilitated by individual throttle bodies. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission shifts with clinical precision, paired with a factory limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance is complete, including documented rod bearing replacement and proactive rear subframe reinforcement. The chassis is dialed in with Bilstein dampers and refreshed bushings, ensuring the 50/50 weight distribution remains razor-sharp. Finished in showroom-quality paint with a flawless interior, this is a turn-key analog masterpiece for the discerning driver.",
